n thousands of lives that were to be laid down over the next year to build it. But what reality was ever made by realists?\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eBuilding this railway is a crime against humanity. It is a factory of death.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003eNecks, continued Colonel Kota, looking away to where an open door framed the rainswept night. That’s all I really see of people now. Their necks. It’s not right to think this way, is it? I don’t know. It’s how I am now. I meet someone new, I look at his neck, I size it up – easy to cut or hard to cut. And that’s all I want of people, their necks, that blow, this life, those colours, the red, the white, the yellow.\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eThis is a samurai’s valour… This is an executioner’s honour…\u003cbr /\u003eThe schmaltzy ending spoilt my overall impression, however.\u003cbr /\u003eWar is a great transformer – it turns ordinary people into torturers and martyrs, into heroes and cowards, into executioners and victims.","rating":4,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/19283284?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2295638880"},"likeCount":159,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":11,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.ma3m7R9Ca9MjT2HT7tXtFw":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.ma3m7R9Ca9MjT2HT7tXtFw","__typename":"Book"},"User:20643658":{"id":20643658,"__typename":"User","legacyId":20643658,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1642506671i/20643658._UX200_CR0,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":691,"viewableName":"°°°·.°·..·°¯°·._.· ʜᴇʟᴇɴ Ροζουλί Εωσφόρος ·._.·°¯°·.·° .·°°° ★·.·´¯`·.·★ Ⓥⓔⓡⓝⓤⓢ Ⓟⓞⓡⓣⓘⓣⓞⓡ Ⓐⓡⓒⓐⓝⓤⓢ Ταμετούρο   Αμ","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/20643658","contributor":null,"isFollowing":fa